name: CRYPTOBIOSIS #001 - TARDIGRADES
description:
A strange creature with a sharp brain and limbs, one of the inhabitants of TRASHVERSE a member of CRYPTOBIOSIS.
The advantages of TARDIGRADES itself are able to live in extreme conditions, have a very tough personality, are able to survive in harsh environments and even vacuum at once.
They can withstand radiation 1000 times the lethal dose to humans, temperatures as low as 300 degrees Fahrenheit or as hot as 300 degrees Fahrenheit.
With this brain-shaped body he is able to engage the brain's performance up to 1000 times faster than the human brain.

This is the first work of the new year 2022 with the hope that everyone can adopt this creature's abilities to navigate this year and years to come.
